<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://ocw.mit.edu/OcwWeb/Economics/index.htm">MIT OpenCourseWare: Economics</a>: Archive of study materials from <a href="MIT" title="MIT" class="mw-redirect">MIT</a> courses</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.economicsnetwork.ac.uk/links/othertl.htm">Online Learning and Teaching Materials</a> UK Economics Network's database of text, slides, glossaries and other resources</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://homepage.newschool.edu/het/thought.htm">Schools of Thought</a>: Compare various economic schools of thought on particular issues</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.econlib.org/">The Library of Economics and Liberty (Econlib)</a>: Economics Books, Articles, Blog (EconLog), Podcasts (EconTalk)</li>
</ul>
</div>
